      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car to tinker with? This vehicle is definitely in a well-loved, 'fixer-upper' state and will need some mechanical and cosmetic work to get it back to its best. It\u2019s an honest ride with plenty of stories to tell, perfect for someone who enjoys a hands-on approach to their next set of wheels!",
