    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s totally ready for your next big adventure? I'm parting with this beauty and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is ready to go today\u2014honestly, you\u2019re going to love it! Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
