      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with recent subframe reinforcement, and the VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. While the finish shows minor patina indicative of its 'good' status, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. Performance is bolstered by a refreshed suspension featuring poly-bushings for improved lateral stability and steering feedback.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Solid engine and transmission. Minimal wear.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained and reliable vehicle that perfectly suits someone looking for quality without the showroom price tag. The exterior features a vibrant finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper. The interior is exceptionally clean and has been kept smoke-free, with the upholstery and carpets showing very little sign of use. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system and climate control, are in full working order. Mechanically, the car is robust; the engine idles smoothly, the transmission is responsive, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has a documented service history, including a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of tires with excellent tread remaining. This is a dependable, attractive car that has been treated with respect and is ready for the road immediately.",
      "price": 29800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
